go to discord.com/Developers/applications
press New application
create your bot name and press create
you press the bot at the bottom left of the screen
you press add bot
and press yes, do it
you go to https://discordapi.com/permissions.html#1099511627775
you tick everything there
you scroll down
and go again to https://discord.com/developers/applications
you press oAuth2
and you copy the client id
you go back to https://discordapi.com/permissions.html#1099511627775
and paste the client id that you copied earlier
after that you press the link under your client id
choose your server
scroll down and press Authorize
verify that you are human
and done
The bot that you create will go directly to your server
